<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1909342-i-haven-t-read-any-of-the-books-in-this">I haven’t read any of the books in this series yet. Should I start in the order published or with this one? TIA</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1909342'><a id="like_count_community_question_1909342" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1909342?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">6 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F50897211-magic-lessons">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
